IN UBUNTU OPEN TERMINAL 
GO TO "NODEJS-HELLOWORLD" FOLDER as downlod repo
INSTALL NPM BY CMD : "npm intall npm"
INSTALL dependencies in package.json by cmd : "npm install"
Now run index.js by cmd : "node index.js"
at now your server is runing on 127.0.0.1:300 you can put at in your browser and see browser and console  you will get message "Hello World"
